Title: Difficulties in a Kind of Averaging Procedure for Constructing
  Gauge-invariant Operators out of Gauge-variant Ones
Authors: Wei-Min Sun, Xiang-Song Chen and Fan Wang
Comments: 3 pages, revtex
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B483 (2000) 299-302
\\
  We prove that a kind of averaging procedure for constructing gauge-invariant
operators(or functionals) out of gauge-variant ones is erroneous and
inapplicable for a large class of operators(or functionals).
